# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:16
translate spanish suzy5_3c671076:

    # "I sit down in the driver's seat and start the car, not yet decided on how I am going to spend the rest of my night."
    "Me siento en el asiento del conductor y arranco el coche, sin haber decidido aún cómo voy a pasar el resto de la noche."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:17
translate spanish suzy5_ed1fbe56:

    # "Then my phone starts buzzing."
    "Entonces mi teléfono empieza a vibrar."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:21
translate spanish suzy5_702d39f2:

    # "I'm not sure who it is, but it is a local number."
    "No estoy seguro de quién es, pero es un número local."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:25
translate spanish suzy5_bea5e8cb:

    # pc "Hello?"
    pc "¿Hola?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:26
translate spanish suzy5_b1036369:

    # ss "Hey [bro], it's me, Suzy."
    ss "Hola, [bro], soy yo, Suzy."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:27
translate spanish suzy5_813bfe8e:

    # pc "Oh hey, [sis]."
    pc "Oh, hola, [sis]."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:28
translate spanish suzy5_6cfa6df6:

    # ss "Could you help me with something please?"
    ss "¿Podrías ayudarme con algo, por favor?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:29
translate spanish suzy5_77c062fa:

    # ss "I'm sitting in the supermarket parking lot and my car won't start."
    ss "Estoy en el aparcamiento del supermercado y mi coche no arranca."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:30
translate spanish suzy5_0c01ea35:

    # ss "I don't know what to do, can you just come help me?"
    ss "No sé qué hacer, ¿puedes venir a ayudarme?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:31
translate spanish suzy5_3c4ee749:

    # pc "Sure, I'm close. I'll be there in a minute."
    pc "Claro, estoy cerca. Estaré allí en un minuto."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:33
translate spanish suzy5_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/suzy_thanks2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/suzy_thanks2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:34
translate spanish suzy5_4ce6f4f0:

    # ss "Thanks."
    ss "Gracias."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:36
translate spanish suzy5_cc61d61a:

    # "I hang up and drive over to the supermarket."
    "Cuelgo y conduzco hasta el supermercado."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:39
translate spanish suzy5_4e12cf19:

    # "I spot Suzy's car pretty quick and park right next to it."
    "Encuento el coche de Suzy enseguida y aparco justo al lado."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:42
translate spanish suzy5_a60d89b8:

    # "Suzy runs up to me immediately after I step out of the car."
    "Suzy corre hacia mí nada más salir del coche."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:43
translate spanish suzy5_96fd56fd:

    # ss "I don't know what happened!"
    ss "¡No sé qué ha pasado!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:44
translate spanish suzy5_4ce21989:

    # ss "I just came out of the store after doing some shopping and it won't start!"
    ss "¡Acabo de salir de la tienda después de hacer la compra y no arranca!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:45
translate spanish suzy5_a56c45eb:

    # ss "I can't afford to take it to a mechanic right now. I barely make anything at Java Lava and Mom is broke."
    ss "Ahora mismo no puedo permitirme llevarlo al mecánico. Apenas gano nada en Java Lava y mamá está sin blanca."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:48
translate spanish suzy5_a9852df6:

    # ss "I hope so. I don't know what I'll do if I don't have my car."
    ss "Espero que sí. No sé qué haré si no tengo mi coche."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:50
translate spanish suzy5_1845952a:

    # ss "Will you look at it please?"
    ss "¿Podrías echarle un vistazo, por favor?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:53
translate spanish suzy5_da8c2e7f:

    # ss "Yes, please. Fix it, [bro]."
    ss "Sí, por favor. Arréglalo, [bro]."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:56
translate spanish suzy5_f393635e:

    # ss "I don't!"
    ss "¡No sé!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:58
translate spanish suzy5_31115693:

    # ss "Can you just see if you can fix it please?"
    ss "¿Podrías ver si puedes arreglarlo, por favor?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:59
translate spanish suzy5_c3f59e51:

    # pc "Yeah, let's see what's up with it."
    pc "Sí, veamos qué le pasa."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:60
translate spanish suzy5_4103549c:

    # ss "Thank you, [bro]. I'm freaking out."
    ss "Gracias, [bro]. Estoy flipando."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:63
translate spanish suzy5_5aa7230b:

    # "I pop the hood and look inside for any problems."
    "Levanto el capó y miro dentro para ver si hay algún problema."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:64
translate spanish suzy5_c9096016:

    # "I'm not really a mechanic or anything and only know a little about cars, but after jiggling a few wires around, I find her battery cable had slid off one of the pegs."
    "No soy mecánico ni nada por el estilo y solo sé un poco de coches, pero después de mover unos cuantos cables, veo que el cable de la batería se había salido de una de las clavijas."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:65
translate spanish suzy5_1ffc433c:

    # "I carefully slide it back down where it is supposed to go and then use one of my keys to tighten the screw so it wouldn't fall off again."
    "Lo vuelvo a colocar con cuidado donde debe ir y luego uso una de mis llaves para apretar el tornillo para que no se vuelva a caer."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:66
translate spanish suzy5_00654239:

    # pc "Go try to start it again."
    pc "Intenta arrancarlo otra vez."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:67
translate spanish suzy5_5c646e65:

    # ss "Okay."
    ss "Vale."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:70
translate spanish suzy5_11b9b96f:

    # "She gets into the driver's side and turns the key and her car starts right up again."
    "Se sube al lado del conductor, gira la llave y el coche arranca de nuevo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:74
translate spanish suzy5_bcd70141:

    # ss "You did it!"
    ss "¡Lo has conseguido!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:75
translate spanish suzy5_8b9f1772:

    # ss "Oh my God, thank you so much."
    ss "Dios mío, muchísimas gracias."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:76
translate spanish suzy5_e161b9ae:

    # ss "Best [brother] ever!"
    ss "¡El mejor [brother] de la historia!"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:79
translate spanish suzy5_86ca1882:

    # "She rushes up and wraps her arms around me, pulling me into a tight hug."
    "Se abalanza hacia mí y me rodea con los brazos, dándome un fuerte abrazo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:82
translate spanish suzy5_7eb555a1:

    # "Then she pulls away, but only slightly, staring up at me with a strange look in her eyes."
    "Luego se aparta, pero solo un poco, mirándome con una extraña expresión en los ojos."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:85
translate spanish suzy5_842415b0:

    # "Without warning, she leans in and put her lips on mine."
    "Sin previo aviso, se inclina y posa sus labios sobre los míos."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:86
translate spanish suzy5_8b1faa90:

    # "It is almost a chaste kiss, but not quite. Her hand is on my chest and there is a passion behind it."
    "Es casi un beso casto, pero no del todo. Su mano está sobre mi pecho y hay pasión detrás de ese gesto."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:87
translate spanish suzy5_8e0321b2:

    # "This isn't just a friendly peck. I feel an urge behind it, like she wants more."
    "Esto no es solo un beso amistoso. Siento un deseo detrás, como si ella quisiera más."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:91
translate spanish suzy5_34527ef1:

    # ss "Uh, sorry."
    ss "Eh, lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:92
translate spanish suzy5_b669988f:

    # ss "I shouldn't have done that, huh?"
    ss "No debería haberlo hecho, ¿eh?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:96
translate spanish suzy5_6cb7ce9a:

    # ss "Really?"
    ss "¿En serio?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:97
translate spanish suzy5_8577d189:

    # pc "No, it was nice."
    pc "No, ha estado bien."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:98
translate spanish suzy5_721098ed:

    # ss "I thought so too."
    ss "Yo también lo creo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:100
translate spanish suzy5_fe4100b4:

    # ss "Anyway, I should go."
    ss "Bueno, me tengo que ir."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:102
translate spanish suzy5_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/suzy_thanks2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/suzy_thanks2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:103
translate spanish suzy5_2ec2b18b:

    # ss "Thanks again, [bro]."
    ss "Gracias de nuevo, [bro]."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:104
translate spanish suzy5_c46a0b54:

    # pc "Any time."
    pc "Cuando quieras."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:106
translate spanish suzy5_bd7daf33:

    # ss "Right. Sorry."
    ss "Vale. Lo siento."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:107
translate spanish suzy5_55a0a639:

    # ss "I should go."
    ss "Me tengo que ir."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:108
translate spanish suzy5_45b1beab:

    # ss "Thanks for fixing my car."
    ss "Gracias por arreglarme el coche."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:112
translate spanish suzy5_f6f30a26:

    # "With that, she gets into her car and I get into mine and we both drive away."
    "Dicho esto, ella se sube a su coche y yo al mío, y los dos nos alejamos conduciendo."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:113
translate spanish suzy5_49ed461b:

    # "What was with that kiss?"
    "¿Qué ha sido ese beso?"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:115
translate spanish suzy5_78e50149:

    # "She definitely seems like she is interested in me. That kiss felt amazing."
    "Definitivamente parece que está interesada en mí. Ese beso ha sido increíble."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:116
translate spanish suzy5_2c26c150:

    # "Somehow, her being my [sister] makes it even hotter."
    "De alguna manera, el hecho de que sea mi [sister] lo hace aún más excitante."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:117
translate spanish suzy5_8ea91748:

    # "I wonder if she would go further?"
    "Me pregunto si iría más allá."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:119
translate spanish suzy5_47e765a1:

    # "She seems like she is actually interested in me romantically."
    "Parece que realmente está interesada en mí sentimentalmente."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:120
translate spanish suzy5_1ec25cb0:

    # "But, she is my [sister], so we can't do anything like that."
    "Pero es mi [sister], así que no podemos hacer nada de eso."

# game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:121
translate spanish suzy5_32823086:

    # "I need to put a stop to this."
    "Tengo que poner fin a esto."

